import React from 'react'

function NewTaskForm(props) {
    return(
        props.clicked ? 
            <form className="new-task-form">
                <input placeholder="New task details" type="text" value={this.state.value}/>
                <select>
                    <option>Code</option>
                    <option>Food</option>
                    <option>Money</option>
                    <option>Misc</option>
                </select>
                <input type="submit" value="Add task"/>
            </form>
            : null
    )
}

export default NewTaskForm
